Package com.atakmap.map.layer.feature

Class FeatureDataSource.FeatureDefinition

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.atakmap.map.layer.feature.FeatureDataSource.FeatureDefinition
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FeatureDefinition, FeatureDefinition2, FeatureDefinition3
    Enclosing interface:
    FeatureDataSource
    public static final class FeatureDataSource.FeatureDefinition
extends java.lang.Object
implements FeatureDefinition3
    The definition of a feature. Feature properties may be recorded as raw, unprocessed data of several well-defined types. Utilization of unprocessed data may yield significant a performance advantage depending on the intended storage.
